For $1-1$, $f(n)=1$, so the sum is $\frac{1}{1}×1=1$;
For $16-81$, $f(n)=2$, so the sum is $\frac{1}{2}×66=33$;
For $256-625$, $f(n)=3$, so the sum is $\frac{1}{3}×369=123$;
For $1296-10000$, $f(n)=4$, so the sum is $\frac{1}{4}×8704=2176$;
For $10001-1995$, $f(n)=3$, so the sum is $\frac{1}{3}×995=332$;
So, $\sum_{k=1}^{1995}\frac 1{f(k)}=1+33+123+2176+332=\boxed{2665}.$</answer>

